 &lt;h1 id=&#34;Format Functions&#34; class=&#34;active&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34;  href=&#34;#Format Functions&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;Format Functions&lt;/h1&gt;

